variables, data types, user input, String, Math, array, multidimensional arrays, if statement, switch statement,
while loop, do while loop, for loop, nested for loop, random, break/continue, recursion, 
class, method, constructor, object, encapsulation, inheritance, polymorphism, inner class, 
abstraction, exception, date, File, ArrayList, LinkedList, Collection,
event handling, mouse handling, JButton, JCheckbox など
